content: mameikagou: Merged two significant PRs this month: #2117 adding name and description to SttTtsPlugin and #2112 fixing unused imports, with substantial code changes totaling +86,279/-45,503 lines across 1,529 files. Created issue #2114 regarding an npm publishing problem for the Twitter plugin, which was subsequently closed. Contributed one code review with approval and made one PR comment, showing focused but sporadic activity concentrated on a single day this month.
